# CLAUDE CODE PROMPT: chrestenson.com Personal Website Build

## PROJECT OVERVIEW

Build an ultra-clean, single-page scroll website for **chrestenson.com** with a bio-hacker/tech-founder aesthetic. The site positions Matthew Chrestenson as an AI-augmented executive strategist and brand architect.

**Live URL:** chrestenson.com  
**Stack:** React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + Vite + GSAP  
**Hosting:** Vercel  
**Repo:** GitHub  

